Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your headband is crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fix it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go. You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day, Mr. Liebert, who emigrated\Nfrom East to West Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared before the media with his wife and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:00:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lieberts showed no signs of exhaustion...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.98,0:01:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and they, along with their fraternal\Ntwins, a son and a daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.78,0:01:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,smiled brightly at the cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert, any opinions about the West?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's difficult to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... now that I can freely express myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find the words to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, the answer to that question...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,lies in the smiles of my wife and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that your children are\Nfully enjoying their freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.85,0:01:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, would you tell us how things really are in the East?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is yours, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:02:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! An acorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Which hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, show me both of your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.29,0:02:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would've been right either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because all the acorns here are yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, brother! Did you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the city from the car on our way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely different from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a lot of pretty stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of different clothes and toys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you saw them too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all yours too, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:03:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they all mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They just are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you on TV, Mr. Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, I wonder if someone's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:04:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you... do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When Uncle Josef and Aunt Klara died...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When Mr. Bodecker died...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a monster came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed them all, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster came to take us away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Put out your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,After you shoot, wipe the gun with a cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and throw it out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you shoot me in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,After you shoot me, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, so the monster won't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I am you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and you are me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That night...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,On that rainy night...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,someone came...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone came to that mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who came?! Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A monster came.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:13.24,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)\pos(360,340)}That Night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this mansion catch fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No one was supposed to be living there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it might've been arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,General Wolf is asking to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,General... Wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,General Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, you were summoned\Nas well, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm waiting at the Red Rose Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter from Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just getting to this hospital here in\NPrague took everything I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you also received a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, only Johan sends letters to the man named Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born into a military family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was guaranteed the path of the chosen at birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the only one who knows me\Nfor what I am is that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the Red Rose Mansion burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're going to emerge...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,into broad daylight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones who had their names\Ntaken from them, like myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to determine the cause of the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it started in the second floor hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from how severely it burned in that area...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,it could've been kerosene or gasoline.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,kerosene?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was arson...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't know for sure until we investigate further, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,there are signs that a wall in the\Nhallway had been torn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw something at the base of the rose\Nbushes, so we started digging, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the bones keep appearing, one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After all these years, they'll finally see the light of day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no one still alive who knows their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It burned down to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This mansion was our only clue to Tenma's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way! Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please contact headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Skeletons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A massive number of human bones were...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty-six people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1981...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,forty-six people suddenly disappeared in that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the little information I was able\Nto obtain in East Germany at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain experiment was being\Nconducted at that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,An experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Step back, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only a theory, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that child was probably born there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't walk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,are we going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, please say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have names.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please say my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please say my...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And something warm to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Johan. It is a wonderful name."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children didn't have names.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps when I gave him the name Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,something inside of him awoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in talking about the past anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about the future, and what will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I no longer have a future...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, General Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to talk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Heinemann is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Heinemann is with someone from our organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Our organization was unified by four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor GÃ¶derich, who was killed, and myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, Eva is with the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to use her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not let them meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I live or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not able to stop them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're about to go berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save them, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Helmut...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmut Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However, those who knew me as Helmut...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,are no longer in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the proof of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmut...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My name...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Helmut Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what Johan saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A world without names...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,General Wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It all burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The gates are locked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The police must've made this place off-limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lipsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this place is important to you because of\Nthe book readings when you were a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This place must have been important to you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It might've been the trigger to recalling\Nyour memories, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That vision...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and piled on top of each other in\Nthe great hall of this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, since the visions you saw were real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised when I saw the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they found the remains of forty-six\Npeople at the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was just as your brother, Johan, told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Johan see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it something horrifying, beyond all imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The true terror?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had been there at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,would I have been the one to become the monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be for the best that this place burned down, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I wouldn't be able to continue\Nliving if I lost this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because this place is full of sad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't an excellent student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't meet his expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I'd been able to meet his expectations...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But reality wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I became an unwanted child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your mom and dad, Mr. Lipsky?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've never lived with them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina's memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If Nina's memories do come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they're happy ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy memories...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happy memories are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you don't have any happy memories,\Nyou can just make some.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma said you can just make them from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, your mouth is covered in ketchup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So is yours, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm creating a new puppet show right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of puppet show is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has ever wanted to see my puppet shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think people will like this next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see your new one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see! I want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a girl who lost her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have dreams that I'm being chased by a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have dreams that I'm chasing after a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I love songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I will have wonderful dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, those dreams will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of what should come after this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make this girl's story have a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make it a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make it a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl decided to embark on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know what kind of journey it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know what lies ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the girl will stay strong and continue her journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl looks back and waves many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, she's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in search of a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, you've come!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you, Mr. Lipsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the son of Franz Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the owner of the Red Rose Mansion, correct?
